'''Thabo Gabriel Malema''' (yavutse 26 Ukuboza 1985), ni umukinnyi wa firime [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika yepfo]] . <ref name="briefly">https://briefly.co.za/69253-thabo-malema-bio-age-wife-wedding-movies-tv-shows-profile.html</ref> Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri firime na ser za televiziyo:''The No. 1 Ladies' Detective Agency'', ''Single Guys'' and ''Strike Back'' . 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 26 Ukuboza 1985 i Mabopane, Gauteng, Johannesburg . Yarangije amashuri yakuye muri kaminuza ya Maryvale. Hanyuma yize firime muri Afrika yepfo ya Motion Picture Medium na Live Performance (AFDA). <ref>https://afternoonexpress.co.za/guests/thabo-malema-/2840</ref> Yakurikiranye kandi impamyabumenyi n'itumanaho muri UNISA.  Mu mwaka wa 2010, yagiye muri Uganda no muri Nigeriya akora muri sosiyete igendanwa ya Airtel. <ref name="GQ">https://www.gq.co.za/culture/entertainment/celebrating-south-african-talent-thabo-malema-42882373</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wo gukina muri 2006 . Yaje gukora film yamateka, ''Kalushi'' .  Iyi filime irazenguruka ku nkuru y’umuhungu ukiri muto, Salomo Mahlangu, winjiye mu mutwe wo kwibohora muri Afurika yepfo nyuma yo gukubitwa n’abapolisi ba apartheid. Mu ikinamico, yakinnye mu ikinamico nka ''All Balls'', ''Umuzi ka Vusi'' na ''Woza Albert'' . Mu mwaka wa 2015, yatorewe igihembo cya Golden Horn igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza mu bihembo bya Filime na Televiziyo bya Afurika y'Epfo (SAFTAs) kubera uruhare rwe nka ''Khaya'' muri filime ''Single Guys'' .  Ariko, azwi cyane kugaragara kuri Agent nka Vuyo no kuri ivu kugeza ivu nka Young Selogilwe Namane. 

Uretse cinema n'ikinamico, kandi yabonekeye mu Televiziyo productions nka ''The Lab'' na ''Room 9,'' single''Guys,'' ''Gold Diggers'' na ''Lithapo.'' Hagati aho, yakoranye na firime mpuzamahanga za Hollywood nka ''Primeval Kill'', ''10 000 BC'' na ''A Million Colors'' .  <ref>https://www.sabcnews.com/sabcnews/feature-thabo-malema-on-the-new-enemy-his-dream-and-covid-19/</ref>

Muri Kanama 2020, yakinnye muri filime yo gusetsa igitsina ''Seriously Single'' afatanije na Katleho Ramaphakela na Rethabile Ramaphakela. <ref>https://www.news24.com/drum/celebs/news/seriously-singles-bohang-moeko-and-yonda-thomas-reflect-on-love-and-dating-20200817</ref> Yasohotse ku ya 31 Nyakanga 2020 kuri Netflix . <ref>http://myheraldmagazine.com/seriously-single-romantic-comedy-premieres-on-netflix-on-31st-july-2020/</ref>

